{"tid":1577912,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［集思廣益］距離9月29號仲有11日 一齊諗口號宣傳全球反共集會","createTime":"2019-09-18T02:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T02:32:53.000Z","uid":213747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"549df1e7fbb5947a56e3ba81caebbbdf250fc046","tid":1577912,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:27:12.000Z","msg":"海外文宣方面(twitter)好似出咗圖都唔多人理我地<br />\n係我杞人憂天定宣傳真係未夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今個weekend嘅屯門光復 元朗靜坐 和你suck等等<br />\n雖然感覺上活動都比較散<br />\n希望各位幫手諗吓有關全球反共嘅口號<br />\n俾各位手足遊行集會嘅時候嗌<br />\n<br />\n另外我覺得下星期要開行個turbo搞國歌晚會<br />\n順手宣傳929反共集會<br />\n盡量爭取國際報導<br />\n<br />\n其實我地唔需要浪費時間去馬場/藍絲集會踩場<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(但我當然唔會阻止去嘅人)</span><br />\n準備好929全球反華集會先係當務之急<br />\n各位手足國事為重啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18adc362c06782e30286af19cfc47e7e4c3cf7c8","tid":1577912,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:27:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f306dbcc8602794fc41c38302cdb6d327d392d9","tid":1577912,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18adc362c06782e30286af19cfc47e7e4c3cf7c8","tid":1577912,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:27:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span 